Hey, take it easy, straw boss.

28
00:01:33,228 --> 00:01:35,234
Now your money's 
better than mine?

29
00:01:35,234 --> 00:01:37,116
I'm just trying to 
get my motor running.

30
00:01:37,116 --> 00:01:38,467
It's Mary's birthday.

31
00:01:38,467 --> 00:01:42,068
I don't call up the full tilt and boogie
tonight, I'll be sleeping on the couch.

32
00:01:44,308 --> 00:01:47,914
Hey, check it out.
Boss man 12 o'clock.

33
00:01:48,139 --> 00:01:50,321
